{
  "id": "S2P01301",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "COMMANDS AND PF KEYS",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You may type information into the COMMAND/OPTION field prior to pressing"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a PF key.  The PF key definition is concatenated ahead of whatever you"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "typed into the COMMAND/OPTION field to form the complete command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Example.  Suppose you define PF12 as an EDIT CHANGE ALL command with"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "no explicit character strings, as follows:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PF12  change all"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Then, in EDIT, you type the following in the command field and press"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PF12 rather than the ENTER key:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND  tct ctc"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The result is exactly the same as if you had typed the following in"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the command field and pressed the ENTER key:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND  change all tct ctc"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
